name: Daikokuten Sama
description: Daikokuten Sama is the god of luck who is the leader of the 7 gods in Japanese legend. Symbolizes luck, wealth and prosperity. The goal of project makes the lives of all those who believe in the project always lucky in life, enrich spiritually ,materially and help people in the world. What will Daikokuten Sama will do? - Education for Community - Marketplace to use $DKKS - Charity Donations - Daikokuten Sama Finance ( Farming, Flash Loan, Staking, NFT Trading, Daiko Wallet) - Entertainment for community ( Lucky Draw, NFT for Art,music)
